data.description: Located in the Palm Harbor subdivision, this Spacious 2700 sqft Pool home offers amenities galore!! Featuring 2 separate living spaces with an open kitchen concept that offers GRANITE COUNTERS, solid WOOD CABINETS with a backsplash and a coffee station/wet bar area! There are 3 Sliding glass doors to access your spacious patio area. The front Living room offers a triple sliding glass door that hides in the wall for a complete indoor/outdoor vibe. A second triple slider off of the other living space and the master bedroom has another slider for a bedroom/patio feel. The Master features a vaulted ceiling with 2 large bathroom vanities, walk in shower and a jacuzzi tub! Tile throughout the main living areas, Carpet in all 4 bedrooms. The open patio provides PLENTY of space for outdoor seating leading to the pool which attaches to the jacuzzi. The back of the home offers a storage shed and outdoor seating area with a fire pit. Some exterior features include a SPRINKLER SYSTEM and Gutters. With all this home offers, you have to come see for yourself. Schedule your showing today!
